extends mail_layout.pug

block content
    h2 Hello #{userName}
    h3 New order
    p 
    | Your order of number 
    - var link = `/order/${orderId}`;
    - var urlDomain = `${domain}`;
    b: a(href=urlDomain + link) #{orderId} 
    | was succesfully created!
    p You can check the details by visiting the link from above.
    p After successfull payment you should receive another email confirmation
    p After receiving the payment, we will ship everything to you as soon as possible
    p In case of any questions, feel free to reach us by e-mail or by phone. All the contact info below
    p Message was generated automatically. Please do not reply to this address